articles.title: Lewandowski fires Barça to La Liga title but invoke Espanyol fans’ wrath - The Guardian
articles.description: Barcelona sealed La Liga by beating neighbours Espanyol 4-2, with Robert Lewandowski scoring two, but fans chased the celebrating visitors off the pitch
